OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLaser brain therapy offers 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhope to epilepsy patients  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hundreds of people with hard-to-treat  
OL,6, epilepsy will be offered laser therapy 
OL,7, targeting the brain on the NHS in      
OL,8, England from next year.                
OL,10,FA tiny laser inside a probe in the     
OL,11,Fskull enables doctors to destroy brain 
OL,12,Ftissue causing seizures.               
OL,14,FThe treatment is more precise and less 
OL,15,Frisky than normal brain surgery and    
OL,16,Fpatients recover more quickly, NHS     
OL,17,FEngland says.                          
OL,19,FCharity Epilepsy Action said the new   
OL,20,Ftherapy was "an exciting ray of hope". 
